NOTICE OF LIEN
The undersigned claims a line upon the property described in the notice for work, materials or
equipment furnished or to be furnished for the improved of the property:
1. The amount of the original contract is: $ _295,000.00
2. The amount of the lien, after deducting all just credits and offsets, is: $295.000.00
3. The name of the owner, if known, of the property is: _ Front Sight Management LLC
4. The name of the person by whom the lien claimant was employed or to whom the lien claimant
furnished or agreed to furnish work, materials or equipment is: _ Top Rank Builders Inc.
5. A brief statement of the terms of payment of the lien claimant's contract is: _ Payments due on draw
6. A description of the property to be charge wit the lien is: _ Single family residence home build
